I watch so many daily try to convince people that they are good or are great or will do it, I’m fascinated by this.

I love to share my ideas, thoughts and concepts in business but with clients or my community or friends or investors or contemporaries I just share my POV and move on.. many disagree with so much I have done in my years in business but at the end of the day, not me nor them is right at that time, history will price out who’s right, debating and trying to convince is very often a energy waster, especially on those who aren’t incentivized to change..

I just move... execute ... hear the doubt and appreciate the support .. but I move.. there’s nothing else.. and I let life be the judge! 

Stop convincing them and start executing on it, that always leads to them “coming over”

🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤

Not just creative control, control, period ... the answer is in the “money” 💰 and it’s not what you think, it’s not amassing money to be able to afford control it’s about saying “no” to money to keep it!
